    <briefdescription>
<para>Forward iterator over live entries. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para><ref refid="classDali_1_1ManagedOpenHashMap_1_1Iterator_1ab4f9bf5d9cbaa49fc136b5a7e2983874" kindref="member">operator*()</ref> — returns <ref refid="structDali_1_1ManagedOpenHashMap_1_1KeyValuePair" kindref="compound">KeyValuePair</ref>&amp; (stable lvalue, satisfies InputIterator) <ref refid="classDali_1_1ManagedOpenHashMap_1_1Iterator_1a3e802a1b12d4310e83cf6a13d1935796" kindref="member">operator-&gt;()</ref> — returns KeyValuePair* (pointer to the same stable object)</para>
<para>Usage: <programlisting><codeline><highlight class="keywordflow">for</highlight><highlight class="normal">(</highlight><highlight class="keyword">auto</highlight><highlight class="normal"><sp/>it<sp/>=<sp/>map.begin();<sp/>it<sp/>!=<sp/>map.end();<sp/>++it)</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">{</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/>DoSomething(it-&gt;key(),<sp/>it-&gt;value());<sp/><sp/><sp/></highlight><highlight class="comment">//<sp/>via<sp/>operator-&gt;</highlight><highlight class="normal"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/>DoSomething((*it).key(),<sp/>(*it).value());<sp/></highlight><highlight class="comment">//<sp/>via<sp/>operator*</highlight><highlight class="normal"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">}</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"></highlight><highlight class="comment">//<sp/>Range-for:</highlight><highlight class="normal"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"></highlight><highlight class="keywordflow">for</highlight><highlight class="normal">(</highlight><highlight class="keyword">auto</highlight><highlight class="normal">&amp;<sp/>kv<sp/>:<sp/>map)</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">{</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/>DoSomething(kv.key(),<sp/>kv.value());</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">}</highlight></codeline>
</programlisting> @SINCE_2_5.20 </para>
    </detaileddescription>
